Jack McGee (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_McGee_(actor) 0 Jack McGee (born February 2, 1949) is an American television and film character actor. He has appeared in over 100 films and television series.McGee is perhaps best known as Chief Jerry Reilly on the television series Rescue Me. He was a regular cast member on the FX series for three seasons. In 2010, he co-starred as Hickey on the Spike TV comedy series Players.
